patch.content: Servers are currently in maintenance to upgrade to the latest patch! Check the latest patch notes here: <https://www.pubg.com/category/patch-notes/>!

voicechat.content: We are aware there are currently issues with the voice chat. This is an issue with Discord and we hope it will be resolved soon.

down.content: Unfortunately, the servers are down right now. Keep an eye on <#289467450074988545> for updates!

report.content:
Want to report an in-game player? Please use the report button in-game as well as sending a ticket via <https://www.pubg.com/support/> 

If you want to report a user on Discord, PM <@407690548401405962> in the sidebar
